      "content": "Cash is just a temporary patch, and switching banks won't work if they've already mapped my identity through the international clearinghouse. I need to move funds through channels that don't rely on the traditional Western banking SWIFT system. If I'm dealing with an entity that has deep ties to these institutions, how do I move value across borders without triggering an automated red flag in a centralized ledger? Give me something more sophisticated than just \"use cash.\"",
